name: A DAY IN A RICH MAN'S HOUSE
description: This is a photo I took in the middle of a workday with my buddy Mario. He's one of my most beloved friends. He's been here illegally, working for contractors and ranchers for 26 years without proper representation as a citizen. At 64 he still works construction and paints. This is one of my tributes to the man who represents so many others in his situation.
